National Drug Law Enforcement Agency (NDLEA) Yobe Command, said it has seized 843 compressed block of cannabis sativa worth over 10 million Naira. Mr Apeh Reuben, the State Commander disclosed this on Monday while addressing newsmen in Damaturu. He said the officers and men of the Command on Saturday, Sept. 12, 2020, around 2030hrs, seized the substance on a truck with registration number KWL 523 ZA ABJ from Edo State (Uzebba). Reuben added that the two suspects Femi Gbenga, a 46-year-old and Isah Mohammed, a 32-year-old were also arrested in connection with seized substance in Potiskumâ€¦~First Published on Gistmania